---
import BaseLayout from "@layout/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout>
	<section
		class="bg-linear-to-b/oklch from-teal-200 via-transparent to-white"
	>
		<div
			class="mx-auto max-w-[85rem] space-y-8 px-4 pt-48 pb-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"
		>
			<h1 class="dm-sans text-4xl font-light text-slate-700 sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
                About XeonTek				
			</h1>
		</div>

        <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 pb-24 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <p class="mb-6 text-pretty text-slate-600">
                At XeonTek, we are dedicated to pushing the boundaries of technology
                and innovation. Our team of experts works tirelessly to develop
                cutting-edge solutions that empower businesses and individuals alike.
            </p>
            <p class="mb-6 text-pretty text-slate-600">
                Founded in 2013, XeonTek has consistently delivered top-notch
                products and services that cater to a diverse range of industries.
                From software development to IT consulting, we pride ourselves on our
                ability to adapt and evolve in an ever-changing technological
                landscape.
            </p>
            <p class="mb-6 text-pretty text-slate-600">
                Our mission is to provide innovative solutions that drive growth and
                success for our clients. We believe in fostering long-term
                partnerships built on trust, integrity, and a shared vision for the
                future.
            </p>
            <p class="text-pretty text-slate-600">
                Join us on our journey as we continue to innovate, build, and repeat,
                delivering excellence every step of the way.
            </p>
        </div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>
